1
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:31,440
Since you won't help

2
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:32,520
I'll do it then.

3
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:34,080
Since you don't wanna get involved in,

4
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:34,840
I'll step up instead.

5
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,600
I'll make sure you stay out of it.

6
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:37,800
Is that okay?

7
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:38,720
Chen Yi.

8
00:01:40,039 --> 00:01:40,680
I'm here.

9
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,000
See Miss Gu home safely.

10
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:54,120
Miss Gu is strange...

11
00:01:54,759 --> 00:01:56,440
You also think so?

12
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:59,400
She's always respectful to you.

13
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,720
But today...

14
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,040
it's like she comes here

15
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:03,400
to have a quarrel.

16
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,600
I reckon she's on purpose.

17
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,240
She wanna save Mrs. Nie and Xiangyun

18
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,640
And she knows I

19
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:12,920
have my reservations.

20
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,440
So she took this chance

21
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:15,440
to have a quarrel with me

22
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:17,320
and let the whole matter drop.

23
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:20,720
If Miss Gu

24
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,440
planned it in this way,

25
00:02:23,079 --> 00:02:24,560
she's really thoughtful.

26
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:44,840
Yes,

27
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:46,120
she is.

28
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,920
With this quarrel,

29
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,120
Mr. Chen is finally separated

30
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,440
from the whole affair.

31
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,600
Yep.

32
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,880
But I haven't thought

33
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:54,200
Lord Nie

34
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:56,280
angered Mr. Chen on purpose.

35
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,320
Miss Gu...

36
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:00,200
Is...

37
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,720
Isn't this

38
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,280
the crime of deceit?

39
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,240
Don't ever

40
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,400
mention this again.

41
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:06,720
Keep it to yourself.

42
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:07,800
Yes, Miss.

43
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,280
How about

44
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,240
Mrs. Nie?

45
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,880
I found an old colleague of Lord Nie

46
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,160
from his days at Tongzhou Garrison

47
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,400
Mr. Lv.

48
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,360
He runs an embroidery workshop.

49
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:17,800
His family fell on hard times

50
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,520
but with fifty taels

51
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,120
Lord Nie gave him back then

52
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:20,960
as startup capital,

53
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,360
he managed to build up the business.

54
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:24,000
I told him about

55
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:24,800
Mrs. Nie's plight

56
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:26,400
and Mr. Lv

57
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,600
agreed to help

58
00:03:27,760 --> 00:03:28,720
right away.

59
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:29,760
He wanna hire Mrs. Nie

60
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:31,240
as an instructor at his workshop

61
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,920
with room and board provided

62
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,760
and one more tael every month.

63
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,000
Does Mrs. Nie

64
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,120
agree?

65
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,079
She's sensible

66
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,000
She said yes the moment I told her.

67
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,160
Tomorrow,

68
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:42,760
I'll have men

69
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:44,040
secretly send her and her daughter

70
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:45,720
to the backyard behind the workshop.

71
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,160
The Nies will never

72
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,120
find them.

73
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,360
Great.

74
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:51,000
This settles

75
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,360
one of my biggest wishes.

76
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,440
Thank you, Mr. Ping.

77
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,360
You're welcome.

78
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:00,800
Aunt,

79
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:03,320
these are premium fried crisp rolls.

80
00:04:03,640 --> 00:04:04,440
Fermented bean curd of Jin's

81
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,760
are in these jars.

82
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,800
These

83
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,200
are all your favorites.

84
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,840
I specially brought them for you.

85
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,200
Once you eat them up,

86
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,960
just let me know.

87
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:14,400
I'll have more delivered right away.

88
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:16,160
Alright, alright.

89
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,760
These are top-grade pine soot ink

90
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,399
and Writing Brush from Huzhou.

91
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,560
These are for Uncle.

92
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,040
You can keep them,

93
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:26,360
or send to others as gifts.

94
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,680
Either way, they're perfect.

95
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,240
Inside this big chest

96
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,400
are all the fabrics

97
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:32,360
Grandma picked out

98
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,200
for Jinzhao.

99
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:35,040
She asked me to bring them along.

100
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:39,760
Good.

101
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:42,120
Very good.

102
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,600
We're family.

103
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:47,440
You've come to the capital to study,

104
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:48,800
and we should look after you.

105
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:49,960
Yet you

106
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:52,159
bring so many gifts.

107
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,400
We're family.

108
00:04:54,840 --> 00:04:55,640
No need for such formality.

109
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:00,480
Tonight,

110
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:02,160
treat Mr. Ji

111
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:03,840
with a slap-up meal

112
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:05,120
at Baiweiju Restaurant.

113
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:07,680
Okay.

114
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,520
By the way, where's Jinzhao?

115
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,520
There's business today

116
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:13,400
and she goes to do with it.

117
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:15,440
Fetch her back at once.

118
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:16,880
Mr. Ji is here.

119
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:18,280
Okay.

120
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:19,440
No hurry.

121
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:26,760
Nanny,

122
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:28,280
go check out the front.

123
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,440
As soon as Jinzhao's back,

124
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:30,880
tell her to come over quickly.

125
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:31,800
Okay.

126
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:44,280
Aunt,

127
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,240
there're some books on my carriage.

128
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:47,400
I don't trust the servants with them.

129
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:48,200
I need to go check.

130
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:48,800
Alright.

131
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:49,840
Suit yourself.

132
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,159
Once you're settled,

133
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:52,000
let nanny take you

134
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,000
to the guest quarters.

135
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:54,840
You must be worn out

136
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:55,680
from the long journey.

137
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,320
Thanks.

138
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,000
Ji!

139
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,080
What's wrong?

140
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,440
Why do you come alone?

141
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:12,440
Where's Grandma?

142
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,920
She's at home.

143
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,080
Is she ill?

144
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,400
I heard lots of trouble broke out at home

145
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,880
because of the land equalization.

146
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,080
She's fine.

147
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,160
Don't worry.

148
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,080
Really?

149
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,120
Don't lie to me.

150
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:31,720
She's really fine.

151
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,200
In a few days,

152
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,159
she'll come to the capital

153
00:06:34,159 --> 00:06:35,640
to deliver Yulin Tuce herself.

154
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,640
Keep it secret.

155
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:37,640
Really?

156
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,280
So...

157
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:40,680
Has the land equalization finished?

158
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:42,400
Great!

159
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:44,800
Ji,

160
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,520
you must be tired.

161
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:46,920
Let me take you to have a rest.

162
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:47,920
No need.

163
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,720
I...I can go by myself.

164
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,520
What happened to you?

165
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:53,159
You've had your coming-of-age ceremony.

166
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:54,720
So...

167
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:55,680
what?

168
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,159
Does that mean

169
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:59,280
we can't

170
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,360
be together?

171
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,320
Where did you pick up such stuffy old-fashioned talk?

172
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:03,880
Stuffy talk?

173
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,880
You're a lady now,

174
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,480
and we're not in Tongzhou.

175
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,840
I'm only doing this

176
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:10,640
for your own good.

177
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:12,680
You're grown up.

178
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:13,920
Time to be sensible.

179
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:15,240
Enough.

180
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:16,400
I'm leaving.

181
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,360
Miss,

182
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,040
what Mr. Ji said does make sense.

183
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,480
Don't be upset.

184
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:28,800
I'm not.

185
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,760
I know he means well.

186
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,320
But in fact,

187
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:34,560
he's not just for my sake.

188
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,480
He's really afraid Grandma

189
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,480
will marry me off to him.

190
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,680
As if I'd ever marry him!

191
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:42,600
Thinks he's such a catch.

192
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,720
Cunshan Academy

193
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:50,040
is famed as No.1 in the capital.

194
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:52,400
It's not easy to study there.

195
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,080
Getting admitted

196
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:56,080
is quite an achievement.

197
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:58,240
It's all thanks to Xuruo.

198
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,880
Had he not written me a recommendation letter,

199
00:07:59,880 --> 00:08:00,680
I'd never get admitted.

200
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,600
Xuruo?

201
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:04,240
Mr. Chen's nephew,

202
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:05,200
Chen Xuanqing.

203
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:11,400
Ji,

204
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:13,880
you'll be schoolmates with Xuanqing?

205
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:15,880
He's done you such a big favor.

206
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:17,520
We must prepare a generous gift

207
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:18,680
to thank him.

208
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:20,480
Grandma has got it ready.

209
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:21,880
I'll take it

210
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:22,520
when registering tomorrow.

211
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:23,680
Okay.

212
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,000
Ji,

213
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,480
you're going to the academy tomorrow?

214
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:28,880
I'll go with you.

215
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,200
What for?

216
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,400
To see you off.

217
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,440
As your younger sister,

218
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,320
I should send you off

219
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,360
to study in the capital.

220
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,360
Jinzhao's right.

221
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,720
If my health weren't so frail,

222
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,840
I'd also go see you off.

223
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:46,440
Let's talk over dinner.

224
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:48,120
Okay.

225
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:49,040
Mr. Ji,

226
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,080
cheers.

227
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:51,720
Jinzhao.

228
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:53,480
I can reach it.

229
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,760
What a future pillar of the nation!

230
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,520
What are you doing, mom?

231
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:03,040
We were having dinner.

232
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,080
Why did you pinch me?

233
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,360
So you felt it huh?

234
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:07,840
I thought you wouldn't notice.

235
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:09,920
Of course I noticed.

236
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,040
I also know

237
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:12,320
you pinched me to make me

238
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,560
go with Jinzhao and Brother Ji

239
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:14,600
to the academy together.

240
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,120
You know it, but still play dumb.

241
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,320
Cause' I don't wanna go.

242
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,040
Why not?

243
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,200
It's such a great chance.

244
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:21,800
Mr. Ji is close

245
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:23,120
with Chen Xuanqing.

246
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:25,560
You know Xuanqing well.

247
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:26,800
If you go along,

248
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:27,880
and spend time with him

249
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,760
after a few meetings,

250
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:31,280
something might come of it.

251
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,040
Come of what?

252
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,560
It's Jinzhao who likes

253
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:36,600
Xuanqing,

254
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,880
not me.

255
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:39,840
What?

256
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:42,240
Jinzhao fancies Chen Xuanqing?

257
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:43,680
Exactly.

258
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:46,840
She told you?

259
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,320
No need.

260
00:09:48,800 --> 00:09:49,880
It's as plain as day,

261
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:50,800
impossible to miss.

262
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:52,280
I've known it for a long time.

263
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,680
No wonder Mrs. Ji

264
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:56,680
cozies up to the Chen.

265
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,960
So that's what she's after.

266
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,200
Though Chen Xuanqing

267
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,520
bears the Chen surname,

268
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:04,040
he is just adopted.

269
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:07,160
What he will achieve

270
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,240
is still uncertain.

271
00:10:08,640 --> 00:10:09,120
Exactly.

272
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:13,280
Lan,

273
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:15,400
I know you have no interest

274
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:16,120
in Chen Xuanqing.

275
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,200
I won't force you.

276
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,640
But you need to understand

277
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:20,680
anyone admitted to Cunshan Academy

278
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:22,240
is not ordinary.

279
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:23,520
You're soon to come of age.

280
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:25,120
Go along tomorrow,

281
00:10:25,280 --> 00:10:26,560
and you might meet a good match.

282
00:10:26,920 --> 00:10:27,720
No.

283
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:30,200
My destiny

284
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:31,480
doesn't lie

285
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,560
in some academy.

286
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:33,720
You...

287
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:43,560
How's he?

288
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,280
He's recovered well

289
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:49,440
and out of danger now.

290
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:51,800
The prescription from the earlier doctor

291
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:52,680
suits his illness.

292
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:53,960
Just keep taking it.

293
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:55,600
However,

294
00:10:55,640 --> 00:10:56,800
his heart condition is treacherous.

295
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,440
From now on, Mr. Ye

296
00:10:58,560 --> 00:10:59,840
must carry his medicine at all times.

297
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:00,840
Don't neglect it.

298
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,040
Thank you.

299
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:04,920
I shall take my leave then.

300
00:11:09,680 --> 00:11:10,520
It seems that

301
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,840
Doctor Xiao's medicine works best.

302
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,160
This works well too.

303
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:16,280
With the Imperial Medical Academy's confirmation,

304
00:11:16,640 --> 00:11:17,480
we'll have

305
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:18,560
a proper reason

306
00:11:18,560 --> 00:11:20,040
to get out of the Eastern Palace.

307
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:21,280
What?

308
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,960
You want me to leave?

309
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:26,080
I've heard Chen Yanyun is strict.

310
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:27,960
He pushes you to study nonstop,

311
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,840
and has you flogged at every turn.

312
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:32,200
Seeing your hands all bruised last time

313
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:33,880
tore my heart apart.

314
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:36,600
The Crown Prince is destined to rule.

315
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,320
You don't need to sit the imperial exam.

316
00:11:38,760 --> 00:11:39,840
Our Marquis Manor

317
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,280
has only you as the sole heir.

318
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:42,800
How can we bear

319
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:43,960
seeing you suffer like this?

320
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:47,320
Come back, okay?

321
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:49,520
I'm not coming back.

322
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:50,240
Why must you

323
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,680
insist on staying in the Palace?

324
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:53,400
But I've already

325
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:54,400
talked to your dad about this.

326
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:55,400
Then go tell him again.

327
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,640
I'm not leaving anyway.

328
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:57,680
But...

329
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:58,440
No buts.

330
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:01,160
Please take your leave, mom.

331
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:03,560
I have a headache.

332
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,000
My Lord,

333
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:28,040
when your heart ailment flared up,

334
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:28,920
it was all thanks to Miss Gu

335
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:29,720
who saved you.

336
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:30,800
Shouldn't we

337
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:33,000
go thank her?

338
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:36,360
You sly lad.

339
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:38,040
You look honest and plain,

340
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:39,280
yet you're quite sharp.

341
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:42,000
But you're right.

342
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,400
I, Ye Xian,

343
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:45,080
never leave a kindness unpaid.

344
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:47,640
Prepare a gift tomorrow.

345
00:12:48,160 --> 00:12:49,400
I'll call on the Gu residence.

346
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:51,360
Okay.

347
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,880
Greetings, Mr. Ye.

348
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,400
My respects, Mr. Ye.

349
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:09,240
Is Gu Jinzhao here?

350
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:10,280
Let her come out.

351
00:13:10,560 --> 00:13:11,680
I have words to say to her.

352
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:14,840
What a pity!

353
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,640
Miss Gu has gone to the academy.

354
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:17,760
Academy?

355
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:19,640
Cousin Ji is

356
00:13:19,640 --> 00:13:21,080
enrolling at Cunshan Academy.

357
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,200
He's registering today.

358
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:24,280
My mom asked her to go along.

359
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:26,880
Why?

360
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:30,120
I have no idea.

361
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:32,640
Maybe now that she's come of age,

362
00:13:32,640 --> 00:13:33,400
she needs to socialize more

363
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:34,560
and go out in society.

364
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:38,960
Socialize, indeed.

365
00:13:40,040 --> 00:13:41,080
Going to a place full of young men

366
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:42,920
perfect for seeking a marriage match.

367
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,520
Please don't put it that way.

368
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:51,680
My Lord,

369
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:52,560
should we head to

370
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:54,000
Cunshan Academy for Miss Gu?

371
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:55,640
Why would I go looking for her?

372
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,360
Am I that bored?

373
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:58,720
Didn't you say

374
00:13:58,720 --> 00:13:59,960
you wanted to repay her kindness?

375
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,680
Who said I wanna repay her?

376
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:17,240
Forget it.

377
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:18,720
In a few days,

378
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:19,800
send her an invitation.

379
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:21,120
Tell her

380
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:23,520
I'm inviting her to dine with me.

381
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:26,440
Yes, my Lord.

382
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:27,720
Giddy up!

383
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:28,760
Giddy up!

384
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,520
What lovely scenery!

385
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,600
Truly an ideal place for studying.

386
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:45,320
It calms the mind and lifts the spirit.

387
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:47,400
Yes.

388
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:49,520
When the old academy head chose the site,

389
00:14:49,680 --> 00:14:51,440
he picked it at once for its hills and rivers.

390
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:53,360
He also sent for craftsmen

391
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,440
all the way from Suzhou to design it.

392
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:56,680
It took five years to complete.

393
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:57,800
No wonder.

394
00:14:58,120 --> 00:14:58,800
If only I could

395
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:00,000
study in such a

396
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,040
wonderful place like this.

397
00:15:01,400 --> 00:15:02,000
I agree.

398
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:03,320
So many women in the world

399
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:05,040
are full of knowledge and talent,

400
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:06,160
yet held back by old customs.

401
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:07,760
To be honest, Miss Gu,

402
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:09,360
the academy head has two daughters.

403
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:11,280
He's long wanted

404
00:15:11,520 --> 00:15:12,640
to find a proper place

405
00:15:12,800 --> 00:15:13,560
and open a school for girls.

406
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:14,640
Really?

407
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:16,080
When that happens,

408
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:17,680
please remember

409
00:15:17,760 --> 00:15:18,520
to let me know.

410
00:15:20,040 --> 00:15:21,000
I'm at the academy too.

411
00:15:21,520 --> 00:15:22,320
If you want to know something,

412
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,320
I can tell you myself.

413
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:24,680
No need to trouble Xuruo.

414
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:25,640
You?

415
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,320
By the time you tell me,

416
00:15:27,520 --> 00:15:28,920
the school will have opened,

417
00:15:29,160 --> 00:15:30,560
and all spots taken.

418
00:15:30,640 --> 00:15:31,600
What do you mean?

419
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:32,280
Do you think

420
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:33,920
I'd stand in your way

421
00:15:33,920 --> 00:15:35,120
and stop you from learning?

422
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,760
I wouldn't put it past you.

423
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:37,880
Two years ago,

424
00:15:37,880 --> 00:15:39,560
I found a nice shop in Baoping.

425
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,520
I just didn't have enough money that day.

426
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:43,080
I'd settled with the owner

427
00:15:43,280 --> 00:15:44,640
to come back the next day.

428
00:15:44,920 --> 00:15:45,600
But then what happened?

429
00:15:45,760 --> 00:15:48,000
You rented it for yourself

430
00:15:48,160 --> 00:15:49,360
with 10% more.

431
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:50,760
Knowing how you love

432
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:51,840
spoiling things for others for no reason,

433
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:52,240
I...

434
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:53,560
who knows what you might do next.

435
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:55,360
I rented that shop

436
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:56,360
for the Ji's own good.

437
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:57,560
Besides,

438
00:15:57,760 --> 00:15:58,160
you only sell

439
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:59,480
rouge and cosmetics anyway.

440
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:00,880
Did you really need such a great shop?

441
00:16:01,160 --> 00:16:02,360
What I sell is none of your business.

442
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:03,520
Snatching what I'm keen on

443
00:16:03,640 --> 00:16:04,840
is simply bad manners.

444
00:16:05,120 --> 00:16:05,840
- I...
- You guys

445
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,000
Inside there

446
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,400
is the reception hall.

447
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:12,520
Sorry for the quarrel, Xuruo.

448
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:13,880
We'll go pay our respects now.

449
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:17,040
Mr. Chen,

450
00:16:18,280 --> 00:16:19,560
I'll wait for you over there.

451
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:21,240
Please take Mr. Ji in.

452
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:22,960
He always

453
00:16:23,160 --> 00:16:24,760
speaks his mind without restraint.

454
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:26,080
I'd be grateful if you

455
00:16:26,280 --> 00:16:27,440
could look after him.

456
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:29,920
There's a pavilion ahead.

457
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:30,960
If you are tired,

458
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:31,920
you can rest there.

459
00:16:32,520 --> 00:16:33,040
Thank you.

460
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:34,360
Let's go.

461
00:16:46,160 --> 00:16:48,960
With gentle breeze and verdant hills,

462
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:52,000
nothing blocks the white clouds flying free.

463
00:16:53,920 --> 00:16:55,560
Mr. Chen wrote this?

464
00:17:02,040 --> 00:17:02,800
Miss Gu.

465
00:17:39,360 --> 00:17:40,280
Mr. Chen?

466
00:17:40,800 --> 00:17:42,040
Why are you alone?

467
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:44,240
Where's Ji?

468
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:46,720
The academy head is testing him.

469
00:17:47,200 --> 00:17:48,360
It's not proper for me to stay there,

470
00:17:48,600 --> 00:17:49,440
so I stepped out.

471
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:54,040
Your calligraphy

472
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:55,600
is truly exquisite.

473
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:57,200
The charm and spirit in it

474
00:17:57,760 --> 00:18:00,240
resemble your father quite a lot.

475
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:01,480
I have indeed studied calligraphy

476
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:02,600
from my father all these years.

477
00:18:02,840 --> 00:18:03,960
Yet even after long practice,

478
00:18:04,400 --> 00:18:05,480
I still fall far short of his skill.

479
00:18:05,840 --> 00:18:07,400
You're too modest.

480
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:09,000
Looking at all the works on this wall,

481
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:10,960
yours is the best.

482
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:13,680
So your father likes to

483
00:18:14,360 --> 00:18:16,400
copy Liu Gongquan's calligraphy.

484
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:17,960
You have a sharp eye, Miss Gu.

485
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:20,320
He admires Liu Gongquan

486
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:22,160
for his open and firm temperament.

487
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:23,960
He says I'm too reserved,

488
00:18:24,120 --> 00:18:25,280
and tells me to practice Liu's style more.

489
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:26,880
Did he ever say

490
00:18:27,120 --> 00:18:28,200
which model to start with

491
00:18:28,440 --> 00:18:30,400
when learning Liu's calligraphy?

492
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,760
Stele Inscription of Xuanmi Pagoda?

493
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:34,560
He likes Vajracchedika-sutra Pagoda.

494
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:31,120
Why on earth

495
00:20:31,120 --> 00:20:32,120
write Vajracchedika-sutra Pagoda?

496
00:20:36,320 --> 00:20:37,640
You're so late!

497
00:20:38,080 --> 00:20:39,200
Obviously you got lectured.

498
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:40,080
I did not!

499
00:20:40,760 --> 00:20:41,680
How did your talk go

500
00:20:42,040 --> 00:20:42,720
with the academy head?

501
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:43,840
He's very kind.

502
00:20:43,960 --> 00:20:44,800
He didn't say too much

503
00:20:45,280 --> 00:20:47,680
but gave me a quite challenging question.

504
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:51,720
What question?

505
00:20:51,960 --> 00:20:52,600
Share with us.

506
00:20:54,800 --> 00:20:56,240
The question

507
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:58,680
is something I've

508
00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:00,560
never thought about before.

509
00:21:05,800 --> 00:21:06,280
Did you

510
00:21:06,520 --> 00:21:07,080
find out anything?

511
00:21:07,360 --> 00:21:08,000
Yes.

512
00:21:08,280 --> 00:21:09,360
That rascal Luo Guier

513
00:21:09,360 --> 00:21:10,280
refused to tell me at first.

514
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:11,480
But once I gave him

515
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:12,360
half a tael of loose silver,

516
00:21:12,360 --> 00:21:13,280
he spilled everything.

517
00:21:13,720 --> 00:21:15,320
He said he didn't see much,

518
00:21:15,800 --> 00:21:16,600
only that when Chen Xuanqing

519
00:21:16,600 --> 00:21:18,080
picked them up from the academy,

520
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:20,000
Miss Gu looked

521
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:21,280
happier than Ji.

522
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:25,960
I knew Miss Gu

523
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:28,080
has her eye on Chen Xuanqing.

524
00:21:58,920 --> 00:21:59,520
Miss,

525
00:22:00,840 --> 00:22:01,360
Miss?

526
00:22:03,360 --> 00:22:04,120
What happened?

527
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:06,360
It's been almost an hour,

528
00:22:06,360 --> 00:22:07,640
and you're still staring at the same page.

529
00:22:08,360 --> 00:22:09,680
Qingpu, let me ask you.

530
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:11,440
What do you

531
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:13,520
think of Chen Xuanqing?

532
00:22:14,720 --> 00:22:16,400
Why bring him up

533
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,560
all of a sudden?

534
00:22:18,440 --> 00:22:19,440
These days,

535
00:22:19,760 --> 00:22:20,800
I've been thinking...

536
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:23,040
If I hadn't found a way myself

537
00:22:23,040 --> 00:22:24,600
to get out of the marriage with Liu,

538
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:26,200
I'd have been married off.

539
00:22:26,760 --> 00:22:27,600
Marrying into that family

540
00:22:27,600 --> 00:22:28,840
would be a lifetime sentence.

541
00:22:31,560 --> 00:22:32,520
In that household,

542
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:34,680
mom's words

543
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:36,000
carry no real weight.

544
00:22:36,760 --> 00:22:37,560
As for my dad,

545
00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:38,520
don't even get me started.

546
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:40,040
I'd be thankful enough

547
00:22:40,040 --> 00:22:41,120
if he doesn't ruin my life.

548
00:22:42,840 --> 00:22:43,640
If I wanna

549
00:22:44,120 --> 00:22:45,560
live a comfortable life,

550
00:22:46,280 --> 00:22:47,360
I must decide

551
00:22:47,560 --> 00:22:48,680
my own marriage.

552
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:51,200
So Miss...

553
00:22:51,360 --> 00:22:52,320
do you mean

554
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:54,000
you fancy Xuanqing?

555
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:59,320
I do think he's quite decent.

556
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:00,720
What do you think, Qingpu?

557
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:03,280
Well...

558
00:23:04,040 --> 00:23:06,280
He's the top provincial scholar,

559
00:23:06,560 --> 00:23:07,440
talented,

560
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:08,280
and gentle in nature.

561
00:23:09,120 --> 00:23:11,120
But he's an adopted son.

562
00:23:11,520 --> 00:23:13,040
I have no idea what life

563
00:23:13,360 --> 00:23:14,440
is really like in the Chen Manor.

564
00:23:47,560 --> 00:23:48,320
No one

565
00:23:48,600 --> 00:23:49,800
is perfect.

566
00:23:51,480 --> 00:23:52,200
Miss Gu.

567
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:57,040
Nanny, what brings you here so late?

568
00:23:57,760 --> 00:23:59,000
Greetings, Miss.

569
00:23:59,840 --> 00:24:01,160
Madam sent me to pass a message.

570
00:24:01,320 --> 00:24:03,160
Grandma will arrive in the capital tomorrow morning

571
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:05,080
Madam's afraid she can't welcome her

572
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:06,040
cause' she feels unwell.

573
00:24:06,320 --> 00:24:08,400
Miss, please go welcome on behalf of her.

574
00:24:09,040 --> 00:24:09,760
Great!

575
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:11,040
Grandma's coming!

576
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:11,720
Yes.

577
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:20,000
So heavy!

578
00:24:20,320 --> 00:24:21,720
Why hasn't Grandma arrived yet?

579
00:24:33,320 --> 00:24:35,160
Wasn't she coming to deliver the Yulin Tuce?

580
00:24:35,560 --> 00:24:36,920
Why are there so many dead bodies?

581
00:24:37,480 --> 00:24:38,480
I'm afraid she's been attacked.

582
00:24:39,760 --> 00:24:40,840
I'll go find Grandma.

583
00:24:41,960 --> 00:24:42,760
I'd like to go too.

584
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:43,760
Stay here.

585
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:45,440
So many have been killed.

586
00:24:48,080 --> 00:24:49,480
Take care, Ji.

587
00:25:08,760 --> 00:25:09,640
Mr. Chen?

588
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:19,600
Miss Gu.

589
00:25:19,760 --> 00:25:20,720
Mr. Chen told me to inform you

590
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:22,400
Mrs. Ji is sorting the accounts,

591
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:23,520
and will be out shortly.

592
00:25:24,360 --> 00:25:25,040
Thank you

593
00:25:25,520 --> 00:25:26,480
and Mr. Chen.

594
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:37,200
Grandma!

595
00:25:52,800 --> 00:25:53,720
Grandma!

596
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,920
Your hair has turned white...

597
00:26:06,080 --> 00:26:07,040
Are you alright?

598
00:26:07,120 --> 00:26:08,360
You scared me to death.

599
00:26:09,680 --> 00:26:11,160
I'm fine.

600
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:15,480
My dear.

601
00:26:37,440 --> 00:26:37,920
Sir,

602
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:40,320
this time in Tongzhou Prefecture,

603
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:41,640
we oversaw Sanhe

604
00:26:41,960 --> 00:26:42,440
Baodi,

605
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:43,440
Wuqing,

606
00:26:43,840 --> 00:26:44,400
Huoxian,

607
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:45,480
these four counties.

608
00:26:46,080 --> 00:26:47,040
After land surveying in full,

609
00:26:47,320 --> 00:26:48,560
a total of 1,363,221 mu
[1 mu≈0.1647 acre]

610
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:50,440
of farmland was registered.

611
00:26:51,360 --> 00:26:52,320
We compiled the Household Registers

612
00:26:52,520 --> 00:26:53,720
and Yulin Tuce,

613
00:26:54,160 --> 00:26:54,880
all storing in sixteen chests.

614
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:56,280
They are all here.

615
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,440
Please

616
00:26:57,680 --> 00:26:58,240
examine them.

617
00:27:00,840 --> 00:27:02,520
Yulin Tuce

618
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:05,040
record every household's land

619
00:27:05,040 --> 00:27:06,600
across our Great Yan.

620
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,560
With these records,

621
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,480
the court can truly

622
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:15,480
control all taxes and corvée nationwide.

623
00:27:15,480 --> 00:27:16,400
Only then do we know

624
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:19,000
how much manpower and resources are needed,

625
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:20,320
and where these

626
00:27:20,320 --> 00:27:21,480
shall be sourced.

627
00:27:21,720 --> 00:27:22,520
Only in this way

628
00:27:23,320 --> 00:27:24,600
can all lands under heaven

629
00:27:24,880 --> 00:27:25,880
be firmly brought

630
00:27:25,880 --> 00:27:28,360
under imperial rule.

631
00:27:28,520 --> 00:27:29,240
This is the foundation

632
00:27:29,960 --> 00:27:32,120
of eternal peace and governance.

633
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:32,720
Great!

634
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:34,680
Great!

635
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:36,440
Congratulations, your Excellency

636
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:37,200
Congratulations, Sir.

637
00:27:44,120 --> 00:27:46,160
Tongzhou has set an example

638
00:27:46,600 --> 00:27:47,640
for the Great Yan.

639
00:27:48,400 --> 00:27:49,360
You have rendered great merit.

640
00:27:49,760 --> 00:27:50,640
And as for

641
00:27:52,040 --> 00:27:52,840
Mrs. Ji,

642
00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:54,080
she deserves great credit.

643
00:27:54,280 --> 00:27:55,320
Together with all the local gentry

644
00:27:55,320 --> 00:27:57,000
who lent their support,

645
00:27:58,200 --> 00:27:59,600
grant them rewards in full.

646
00:28:02,120 --> 00:28:02,760
I

647
00:28:03,200 --> 00:28:04,040
speak on behalf of Mrs. Ji

648
00:28:04,280 --> 00:28:05,200
to thank you, Sir.

649
00:28:07,560 --> 00:28:08,520
It is only a pity...

650
00:28:08,920 --> 00:28:09,560
What's wrong?

651
00:28:10,600 --> 00:28:11,400
I cannot help

652
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:13,200
thinking of Fengming.

653
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:22,040
You've always been

654
00:28:24,240 --> 00:28:25,560
a man of loyalty and sentiment.

655
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:27,440
Yet the time

656
00:28:28,560 --> 00:28:30,800
has not come to petition rewards for him.

657
00:28:33,280 --> 00:28:33,800
Yes, Sir.

658
00:28:36,080 --> 00:28:37,600
How goes the investigation into

659
00:28:37,600 --> 00:28:38,640
Your Highness' assassination?

660
00:28:39,120 --> 00:28:41,320
Xiao Qishan has been investigated.

661
00:28:41,440 --> 00:28:42,400
No report has returned.

662
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:43,760
But I have given strict orders:

663
00:28:44,280 --> 00:28:45,400
Bring him back alive,

664
00:28:45,880 --> 00:28:46,960
or bring back his body.

665
00:28:48,280 --> 00:28:49,600
Make the search thorough.

666
00:28:51,160 --> 00:28:52,200
Now that

667
00:28:53,600 --> 00:28:55,520
His Majesty gets older,

668
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:58,560
he has grown far more lenient.

669
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:00,240
Prince Glorian is the

670
00:29:00,440 --> 00:29:02,480
late Prince Chengqing's younger brother,

671
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:04,440
and His Majesty's only living sibling.

672
00:29:04,600 --> 00:29:05,640
To move against him,

673
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:09,760
we must have irrefutable proof.

674
00:29:11,520 --> 00:29:12,080
Okay.

675
00:29:20,720 --> 00:29:21,280
You!

676
00:29:21,680 --> 00:29:23,520
You insolent little brute!

677
00:29:23,920 --> 00:29:24,640
Might as well

678
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:25,600
have it put down at once.

679
00:29:26,760 --> 00:29:27,160
Wait!

680
00:29:29,080 --> 00:29:29,800
Uncle Li,

681
00:29:30,040 --> 00:29:31,480
it was wrong for Frost to bite you,

682
00:29:31,760 --> 00:29:33,040
but it just bit through your clothes.

683
00:29:33,320 --> 00:29:34,640
Not even a tooth mark was left.

684
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:36,200
Must you be so unforgiving?

685
00:29:36,280 --> 00:29:37,800
You're indeed clever.

686
00:29:39,400 --> 00:29:40,200
Does...

687
00:29:44,320 --> 00:29:45,240
this mean...

688
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:47,040
in your opinion,

689
00:29:47,040 --> 00:29:48,320
I must wait until the brute

690
00:29:48,320 --> 00:29:50,720
bites me till I bleed,

691
00:29:51,080 --> 00:29:53,440
before I may punish it?

692
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:54,840
That is not what I meant.

693
00:29:56,280 --> 00:29:58,160
Indeed, Prince Glorian.

694
00:29:58,480 --> 00:29:59,280
Son of a bitch!

695
00:30:00,520 --> 00:30:01,000
You!

696
00:30:01,320 --> 00:30:03,400
I'm speaking with him.

697
00:30:03,760 --> 00:30:05,160
When did you get leave to interrupt?

698
00:30:06,720 --> 00:30:08,360
You deserve to be beaten to death.

699
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:09,240
Guards!

700
00:30:09,920 --> 00:30:10,480
Hold on!

701
00:30:13,160 --> 00:30:13,920
Minister Ye!

702
00:30:22,280 --> 00:30:23,120
Greetings, Your Highness.

703
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:24,840
Greetings, Prince Glorian.

704
00:30:26,040 --> 00:30:28,440
So you are the one unfit for martial arts,

705
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:29,560
unable to go to the battlefield—

706
00:30:29,560 --> 00:30:31,040
the heir of Lord Changxing?

707
00:30:33,040 --> 00:30:34,720
Ye Guangsheng enjoyed a lifetime of fame.

708
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:35,880
What a pity!

709
00:30:36,080 --> 00:30:36,920
One wonders

710
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,400
if this is his retribution.

711
00:30:40,480 --> 00:30:42,160
I never thought you believed in karma.

712
00:30:42,600 --> 00:30:43,600
If so,

713
00:30:44,080 --> 00:30:46,120
the sudden death of your heir of Lord Chongguang in Tongzhou

714
00:30:47,360 --> 00:30:48,800
must also be your karma.

715
00:30:49,280 --> 00:30:49,720
You!

716
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:55,280
What a sharp tongue you have!

717
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:56,440
What are you doing here?

718
00:30:58,240 --> 00:30:59,680
Frost has been unwell.

719
00:31:00,320 --> 00:31:01,920
His Highness sent me to check on it.

720
00:31:02,840 --> 00:31:04,400
I didn't expect just as it caused trouble.

721
00:31:04,640 --> 00:31:05,720
May I ask where

722
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:07,480
Frost bit you?

723
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:09,760
Your Highness,

724
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:11,280
it was by the outer wall

725
00:31:11,280 --> 00:31:12,880
at the north corner gate of the Eastern Palace.

726
00:31:13,160 --> 00:31:14,440
Frost had indigestion,

727
00:31:14,560 --> 00:31:16,360
and I was walking it there.

728
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:17,040
Then

729
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:19,160
we met Prince Glorian.

730
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:21,800
The north corner gate of the Eastern Palace...

731
00:31:23,120 --> 00:31:24,520
It is very remote.

732
00:31:25,280 --> 00:31:25,960
May I ask why you

733
00:31:25,960 --> 00:31:27,040
went all the way out there?

734
00:31:27,760 --> 00:31:28,400
Yes.

735
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:29,960
I almost forgot to ask.

736
00:31:30,560 --> 00:31:32,320
Uncle Li, why would you

737
00:31:32,960 --> 00:31:34,120
go outside the Eastern Palace?

738
00:31:35,680 --> 00:31:36,320
I

739
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:38,160
entered the palace to congratulate His Majesty

740
00:31:38,360 --> 00:31:39,880
on the successful land equalization in Tongzhou.

741
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:40,960
On my way out,

742
00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:42,680
I just passed by the Eastern Palace.

743
00:31:44,360 --> 00:31:45,400
What a fortunate "coincidence"

744
00:31:45,840 --> 00:31:46,960
you have!

745
00:31:47,600 --> 00:31:47,960
You...

746
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:48,520
Yes.

747
00:31:49,360 --> 00:31:51,680
Uncle, coming all the way to this remote place,

748
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:53,680
what business do you have here?

749
00:31:54,760 --> 00:31:56,080
Why did you not send word beforehand?

750
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:58,480
Does my Father know your visit?

751
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:01,120
I just think the weather is fine

752
00:32:01,120 --> 00:32:02,160
and come out for a stroll.

753
00:32:02,760 --> 00:32:04,040
I don't think there's a need.

754
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:09,520
It is 12 o'clock.

755
00:32:10,040 --> 00:32:10,960
I have other affairs to attend to,

756
00:32:11,600 --> 00:32:12,320
and shall not waste time

757
00:32:12,320 --> 00:32:13,200
bickering here.

758
00:32:14,920 --> 00:32:16,000
Goodbye.

759
00:32:20,360 --> 00:32:20,920
Stand up.

760
00:32:22,800 --> 00:32:23,360
Ye Xian,

761
00:32:24,000 --> 00:32:25,440
what do you make of that old fox

762
00:32:25,560 --> 00:32:26,520
sneaking around

763
00:32:27,800 --> 00:32:29,120
outside the Eastern Palace?

764
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:32,920
I dare not speculate.

765
00:32:33,320 --> 00:32:34,120
You dare not?

766
00:32:34,280 --> 00:32:34,880
Then I dare.

767
00:32:35,600 --> 00:32:36,640
Maybe this guy

768
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:38,080
was scouting the place.

769
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:38,960
Your Highness,

770
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:40,040
don't...

771
00:32:40,160 --> 00:32:41,000
What are you afraid of?

772
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:41,920
Ye Xian is one of us.

773
00:32:55,800 --> 00:32:56,480
Mom.

774
00:32:59,400 --> 00:33:00,760
Having the two of you

775
00:33:00,760 --> 00:33:02,080
attending to me like this,

776
00:33:02,280 --> 00:33:03,560
somehow I feel

777
00:33:03,560 --> 00:33:04,600
ill at ease.

778
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:05,920
Alright, alright.

779
00:33:06,120 --> 00:33:07,600
Sit down and rest.

780
00:33:07,800 --> 00:33:09,000
Let Jinzhao rest.

781
00:33:09,160 --> 00:33:10,680
It has been so long since we met.

782
00:33:10,680 --> 00:33:11,800
I wanna attend to you and show my filial piety.

783
00:33:12,400 --> 00:33:13,400
I won't!

784
00:33:13,560 --> 00:33:14,360
I wanna stay right here

785
00:33:14,360 --> 00:33:15,280
and look after Grandma.

786
00:33:16,560 --> 00:33:17,880
Very well, dear.

787
00:33:19,040 --> 00:33:19,600
Mom,

788
00:33:20,520 --> 00:33:22,680
can you stay a few more days this time?

789
00:33:24,040 --> 00:33:25,360
I'm afraid not.

790
00:33:26,080 --> 00:33:27,800
I've come on official business.

791
00:33:28,120 --> 00:33:29,160
Early tomorrow morning,

792
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:31,920
I need to go to the Chen Manor to visit Mr. Chen.

793
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:35,840
The land equalization in Tongzhou went smoothly.

794
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:39,120
Next will be Beizhili.

795
00:33:39,840 --> 00:33:42,040
I suspect Mr. Chen wanted me

796
00:33:42,400 --> 00:33:44,160
to take charge of the next task.

797
00:33:44,560 --> 00:33:45,520
After all,

798
00:33:45,840 --> 00:33:47,000
I've had the experience.

799
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:49,680
But...

800
00:33:49,840 --> 00:33:51,480
Mr. Chen really ought not to.

801
00:33:52,200 --> 00:33:54,000
Land equalization is dangerous enough as it is,

802
00:33:54,560 --> 00:33:56,000
and you're up in years.

803
00:33:56,240 --> 00:33:57,880
Why treat you like an able-bodied laborer?

804
00:33:59,280 --> 00:34:01,320
There's no other choice.

805
00:34:02,000 --> 00:34:02,720
Grandma,

806
00:34:03,040 --> 00:34:04,760
Let me go with you tomorrow.

807
00:34:06,800 --> 00:34:07,640
Okay.

808
00:34:09,040 --> 00:34:10,239
At your age,

809
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:11,360
you ought to go out

810
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:12,760
and see more of the world.

811
00:34:17,080 --> 00:34:18,280
The land equalization in Tongzhou

812
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:19,400
was a great success.

813
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:21,320
When Lord Chief Councilor spoke of your merits

814
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,480
to His Majesty,

815
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:24,480
he was greatly pleased.

816
00:34:25,040 --> 00:34:25,760
You'll

817
00:34:26,320 --> 00:34:27,560
be granted official rewards shortly.

818
00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:28,880
I merely followed

819
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:30,760
Mr. Chen's instructions.

820
00:34:31,239 --> 00:34:32,360
I dare not claim any credit.

821
00:34:32,639 --> 00:34:34,159
Lord Chief Councilor intends that

822
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:35,280
one province in the south

823
00:34:35,560 --> 00:34:37,239
and one in the north

824
00:34:38,080 --> 00:34:40,440
shall be chosen for further pilot.

825
00:34:42,520 --> 00:34:43,320
Grandma!

826
00:34:44,520 --> 00:34:45,360
Jinzhao,

827
00:34:46,199 --> 00:34:47,679
what brings you here?

828
00:34:50,960 --> 00:34:51,920
Greetings, Sir.

829
00:34:52,639 --> 00:34:53,639
I saw Mrs. Chen

830
00:34:53,639 --> 00:34:54,560
growing anxious waiting,

831
00:34:54,920 --> 00:34:55,920
so I volunteered

832
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:56,920
to come fetch you.

833
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:00,920
My old friend

834
00:35:01,160 --> 00:35:03,160
has always been impetuous.

835
00:35:03,600 --> 00:35:04,240
Sir,

836
00:35:04,600 --> 00:35:06,520
I shall take my leave first.

837
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:09,080
Okay.

838
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:11,560
If I have any doubts

839
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:13,320
about official affairs in days to come,

840
00:35:13,560 --> 00:35:14,800
I shall seek your counsel.

841
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:17,400
You flatter me.

842
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:41,800
Mr. Chen, your ink bamboo painting

843
00:35:42,120 --> 00:35:43,760
grows ever more vivid and lifelike.

844
00:35:49,160 --> 00:35:50,120
Sir.

845
00:35:50,720 --> 00:35:51,560
You're here.

846
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:52,800
Come in and speak.

847
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:55,440
You knew I'd come?

848
00:35:55,720 --> 00:35:56,880
Your manner just now

849
00:35:57,280 --> 00:35:58,600
shows you have something on your mind.

850
00:35:59,440 --> 00:36:00,640
Speak. What do you seek of me?

851
00:36:01,280 --> 00:36:02,560
I beg you

852
00:36:02,880 --> 00:36:03,960
not to send my grandma

853
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:05,360
to take part in the land equalization of Beizhili.

854
00:36:12,680 --> 00:36:14,760
Did your grandma send you to say this?

855
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:16,120
No, no, no.

856
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:18,960
It is my own thoughts.

857
00:36:19,560 --> 00:36:20,800
Then your grandma must have

858
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:22,520
spoken to you about Beizhili's affairs.

859
00:36:22,680 --> 00:36:23,320
Nope.

860
00:36:24,240 --> 00:36:25,520
She has never told me

861
00:36:25,520 --> 00:36:27,160
anything about land equalization.

862
00:36:27,840 --> 00:36:29,040
I figured it out myself.

863
00:36:30,640 --> 00:36:31,440
I reasoned that

864
00:36:31,640 --> 00:36:33,960
now that it has succeeded in Tongzhou,

865
00:36:34,120 --> 00:36:36,000
the next task might be Beizhili.

866
00:36:36,680 --> 00:36:39,520
Then it will continue south along the Grand Canal.

867
00:36:40,040 --> 00:36:41,320
You know far more than I expected.

868
00:36:42,240 --> 00:36:43,480
You once told me

869
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:45,520
land equalization is a grave state affair,

870
00:36:46,160 --> 00:36:47,040
and since ancient times,

871
00:36:47,280 --> 00:36:48,520
it has never been achieved without bloodshed.

872
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:50,560
In Tongzhou this time,

873
00:36:51,080 --> 00:36:51,680
it nearly cost

874
00:36:51,680 --> 00:36:53,040
Grandma half her life.

875
00:36:55,600 --> 00:36:56,320
I am afraid...

876
00:36:58,320 --> 00:36:59,120
I...

877
00:37:02,240 --> 00:37:03,240
I beg you to

878
00:37:03,520 --> 00:37:04,480
let my Grandma

879
00:37:04,720 --> 00:37:06,520
retire from all land equalization duties.

880
00:37:07,440 --> 00:37:08,840
I can take over all

881
00:37:09,080 --> 00:37:10,520
of Grandma's responsibilities.

882
00:37:11,080 --> 00:37:12,560
If blood must be shed,

883
00:37:13,200 --> 00:37:14,280
let it be mine.

884
00:37:15,960 --> 00:37:16,640
You?

885
00:37:20,560 --> 00:37:21,400
You cannot take the place

886
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:22,360
of your Grandma.

887
00:37:23,120 --> 00:37:23,920
I can!

888
00:37:24,440 --> 00:37:25,560
Everyone knows

889
00:37:25,720 --> 00:37:26,840
Grandma dotes on me most.

890
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:28,120
If I stand forth

891
00:37:28,320 --> 00:37:29,800
on behalf of Grandma and the Jis,

892
00:37:30,040 --> 00:37:31,160
all will trust me.

893
00:37:31,680 --> 00:37:32,320
Furthermore,

894
00:37:32,560 --> 00:37:33,920
whether it be contacting local gentry,

895
00:37:34,240 --> 00:37:35,560
or planning calculations,

896
00:37:35,760 --> 00:37:36,520
I am fully capable.

897
00:37:37,520 --> 00:37:39,560
I know the lands of Beizhili well.

898
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:41,160
If there is anything I do not know,

899
00:37:41,600 --> 00:37:42,840
I can consult my Grandma.

900
00:37:43,440 --> 00:37:44,560
Listening to you,

901
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:46,600
one would think land equalization

902
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:47,960
is a trivial matter

903
00:37:48,120 --> 00:37:49,000
anyone can do.

904
00:37:49,160 --> 00:37:50,600
It is surely no easy task,

905
00:37:51,240 --> 00:37:52,040
but

906
00:37:52,720 --> 00:37:53,800
I'm willing to learn.

907
00:37:54,280 --> 00:37:55,360
Grandmother is advanced in years,

908
00:37:56,040 --> 00:37:57,080
her strength fading.

909
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:59,000
I am still young,

910
00:37:59,600 --> 00:38:00,480
and fear no hardship

911
00:38:00,720 --> 00:38:01,680
in traveling to and fro.

912
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,080
Miss Gu,

913
00:38:03,600 --> 00:38:05,120
this is a matter of imperial court importance,

914
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:06,080
not a trifling matter.

915
00:38:07,880 --> 00:38:08,440
Chen Yi.

916
00:38:09,240 --> 00:38:09,920
Sir!

917
00:38:10,240 --> 00:38:11,480
Grandma is old,

918
00:38:11,920 --> 00:38:12,720
and she has never

919
00:38:12,960 --> 00:38:14,440
spent a day of peace and leisure.

920
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:15,560
Please.

921
00:38:15,920 --> 00:38:17,360
spare my grandmother from this toil.

922
00:38:17,680 --> 00:38:18,320
Show her out.

923
00:38:19,480 --> 00:38:20,000
Yes, Sir.

924
00:38:20,680 --> 00:38:21,440
Miss Gu,

925
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:22,480
this way please.

926
00:38:53,200 --> 00:38:53,880
Sir,

927
00:38:54,600 --> 00:38:55,800
had you not decided

928
00:38:55,800 --> 00:38:57,600
to have Mrs. Ji write down

929
00:38:57,600 --> 00:38:58,560
Tongzhou's experience

930
00:38:58,960 --> 00:39:00,560
and spare her from Beizhili?

931
00:39:01,120 --> 00:39:02,360
This is a matter of great gravity.

932
00:39:03,440 --> 00:39:05,120
I can excuse her from going,

933
00:39:05,440 --> 00:39:06,040
yet I can't yield to her plea.

934
00:39:06,040 --> 00:39:07,200
If I grant her wish after that,

935
00:39:07,360 --> 00:39:08,760
what will the court make of me?

936
00:39:09,520 --> 00:39:10,960
I can't help but feel

937
00:39:11,560 --> 00:39:13,040
you were just teasing Miss Gu.

938
00:39:19,680 --> 00:39:20,520
By the way,

939
00:39:21,280 --> 00:39:23,400
Mrs. Chen asked me the other day

940
00:39:23,920 --> 00:39:25,880
to arrange a marriage for you,

941
00:39:26,760 --> 00:39:28,200
and bid me ask you.

942
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:32,760
Right,

943
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:38,120
I heard of the southwest a few days ago.

944
00:39:38,720 --> 00:39:40,280
There seems to be a lead on Xiao Qishan.

945
00:39:40,760 --> 00:39:41,560
I think

946
00:39:42,520 --> 00:39:43,880
you need to go there in person.

947
00:39:44,520 --> 00:39:45,400
Is that okay?

948
00:39:46,320 --> 00:39:47,960
The New Year is coming,

949
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:49,560
and bandits run rampant in the southwest.

950
00:39:51,840 --> 00:39:52,840
Delay will be dangerous.

951
00:39:53,440 --> 00:39:54,440
Set off tomorrow.

952
00:39:59,640 --> 00:40:00,440
Okay.

953
00:40:02,120 --> 00:40:03,520
Might as well return to my hometown.

954
00:40:05,880 --> 00:40:07,120
Such a petty mind.

955
00:40:07,680 --> 00:40:08,640
Take care of yourself.

956
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:15,160
Holding such a high office,

957
00:40:15,680 --> 00:40:16,880
yet he remains so petty.

958
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:19,040
Not even a single room

959
00:40:19,040 --> 00:40:19,840
for discussion.

960
00:40:23,040 --> 00:40:24,000
Xuanqing?

961
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:25,120
Miss Gu?

962
00:40:32,320 --> 00:40:34,120
I returned to the manor to fetch a few books today,

963
00:40:34,520 --> 00:40:35,280
never expecting

964
00:40:35,280 --> 00:40:36,280
to meet you here.

965
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:40,040
I came with my grandma

966
00:40:40,320 --> 00:40:41,920
to pay respects to Mrs. Chen.

967
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:44,720
Xuanqing,

968
00:40:45,160 --> 00:40:46,360
what book are you reading?

969
00:40:55,200 --> 00:40:57,160
Better be deemed cunning than a false loyalist.

970
00:40:58,440 --> 00:41:01,000
Better be unyielding than a worldly conformist.

971
00:41:01,000 --> 00:41:02,080
This book is interesting.

972
00:41:02,680 --> 00:41:03,760
Its criticisms are refreshingly blunt.

973
00:41:09,080 --> 00:41:11,120
Are you in a hurry to read this book?

974
00:41:12,200 --> 00:41:12,600
Xuanqing,

975
00:41:13,080 --> 00:41:13,960
there you are.

976
00:41:14,240 --> 00:41:15,080
I've been searching for you.

977
00:41:16,040 --> 00:41:16,800
Miss Gu.

978
00:41:19,640 --> 00:41:20,360
There's no hurry.

979
00:41:21,120 --> 00:41:22,160
If you like it,

980
00:41:22,320 --> 00:41:23,400
just take it and read it.

981
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:26,120
Fine, thank you.

982
00:41:28,880 --> 00:41:29,880
I have to go.

983
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:31,520
My Grandma is waiting for me.

984
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:32,600
Okay.

985
00:41:46,040 --> 00:41:46,320
Giddy up!

986
00:41:47,040 --> 00:41:47,760
Giddy up!

987
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:49,120
Giddy up!

988
00:41:49,400 --> 00:41:50,280
Miss Qingpu, wait a moment.

989
00:41:51,720 --> 00:41:52,560
Stop.

990
00:41:56,920 --> 00:41:57,600
Miss Qingpu,

991
00:41:57,920 --> 00:41:58,640
Mr. Chen  sent me

992
00:41:58,800 --> 00:42:00,040
with a letter for Mrs. Ji.

993
00:42:15,760 --> 00:42:16,600
Grandma,

994
00:42:17,400 --> 00:42:19,320
what does the letter read?

995
00:42:23,040 --> 00:42:24,160
It read that

996
00:42:25,080 --> 00:42:26,360
considering my advanced age,

997
00:42:26,920 --> 00:42:28,520
the Jis is excused

998
00:42:29,400 --> 00:42:31,480
from further land equalization affairs.

999
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:33,280
I just need to record my experience

1000
00:42:33,640 --> 00:42:34,920
in a book,

1001
00:42:35,680 --> 00:42:37,520
and hand it in to the court.

1002
00:42:37,680 --> 00:42:38,360
Really?

1003
00:42:38,920 --> 00:42:39,800
That's great!

1004
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:41,720
You can finally

1005
00:42:42,160 --> 00:42:43,280
rest from all that traveling and toil.

1006
00:42:44,400 --> 00:42:45,000
Yes.

1007
00:42:46,480 --> 00:42:47,800
It seems Mr. Chen

1008
00:42:49,160 --> 00:42:51,800
does have consideration for the Jis.

1009
00:43:01,240 --> 00:43:02,560
Grandma returns

1010
00:43:03,800 --> 00:43:05,200
to Tongzhou tomorrow,

1011
00:43:05,200 --> 00:43:06,360
and you need to get up early.

1012
00:43:07,320 --> 00:43:09,000
Xuanqing never set a fixed date

1013
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:10,280
for the book's return.

1014
00:43:10,600 --> 00:43:11,600
Why stay up

1015
00:43:11,600 --> 00:43:12,920
poring over it by lamp light?

1016
00:43:13,200 --> 00:43:14,760
You'll strain your eyes.

1017
00:43:15,720 --> 00:43:16,680
Now that Grandma

1018
00:43:16,680 --> 00:43:18,280
can head back to Tongzhou safe and sound,

1019
00:43:18,560 --> 00:43:19,600
my heart is at peace too.

1020
00:43:20,480 --> 00:43:21,520
But for this book,

1021
00:43:21,680 --> 00:43:22,440
Xuanqing went all the way back

1022
00:43:22,440 --> 00:43:24,080
from the academy just to fetch it.

1023
00:43:25,160 --> 00:43:26,600
It must matter.

1024
00:43:27,000 --> 00:43:28,520
He kindly lent it to me,

1025
00:43:28,960 --> 00:43:30,680
and I cannot be ungrateful.

1026
00:43:31,320 --> 00:43:32,680
I must finish it quickly

1027
00:43:32,920 --> 00:43:33,680
and return it to him.

1028
00:43:38,640 --> 00:43:39,640
What are you laughing at?

1029
00:43:41,200 --> 00:43:43,440
I'm laughing at how you keep saying "he" about Xuanqing.

1030
00:43:43,960 --> 00:43:45,720
You've said it three times.

1031
00:43:47,240 --> 00:43:48,160
I'm just saying.

1032
00:43:48,840 --> 00:43:50,000
Hurry and grind the ink.
